{"tid":1234461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有兩個回覆非常值得貼堂","createTime":"2019-06-17T02:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T02:30:03.000Z","uid":1834,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d1291f2f05bdcd3103aa32f99742a139cf9cc7eb","tid":1234461,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/scCCP9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FscCCP9k.png&h=b344ca0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4AqwUA1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4AqwUA1.png&h=4d07bc07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n勇武衝完有成果就坐享其成<br />\n之後左膠一輪後就階段性勝利<br />\n仲要一邊話和理非同勇武並用，一邊割𥱊<br />\n<br />\n呢兩段只係小數<br />\n我希望香港人唔好再咁易畀風向帶到<br />\n自己用下腦諗清楚下一步可以做咩"},{"pid":"04d815cf179e81954e17da70085824105222dabe","tid":1234461,"uid":143210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:24:03.000Z","msg":"失敗主義不是無為的理由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234103</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望經過今次大家學識抱打不平，友善照舊，有錯就要講！<br />\n<br />\n分化輿論要由我地親手阻止<br />\n<br />\n戰場唔止熱門仲有係最新"},{"pid":"7fe15e84fa34acb4c227cc2563f7b009bdca9f62","tid":1234461,"uid":1834,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"04d815cf179e81954e17da70085824105222dabe","tid":1234461,"uid":143210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:24:03.000Z","msg":"失敗主義不是無為的理由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234103</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望經過今次大家學識抱打不平，友善照舊，有錯就要講！<br />\n<br />\n分化輿論要由我地親手阻止<br />\n<br />\n戰場唔止熱門仲有係最新"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:25:04.000Z","msg":"停啦好嗎？洗撚夠未"},{"pid":"33d4d1f2d76c68a7a0e62bc2bfe7ab98940a816b","tid":1234461,"uid":953,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:28:26.000Z","msg":"請大家不要分化<br />\n如果唔係612班義士<br />\n616 就唔